004package data;
005
006/** Simulation parameters. */
007public class SimParams {
008  /**
009   * Returns bases for simulation.
010   * @param mdId Model identifier.
011   * @return Ditto.
012   */
013  public static double[] paramBases (String mdId) {
014    if(mdId.equals("APRX")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.005};
015    if(mdId.equals("APRX2")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.005};
016    if(mdId.equals("APRX3")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.005};
017    if(mdId.equals("ME")) return new double[]{5.0, 0.01};
018    if(mdId.equals("ME2")) return new double[]{5.0, 0.01};
019    if(mdId.equals("MM")) return new double[]{5.0, 0.01};
020    if(mdId.equals("MX_MN")) return new double[]{5.0, 0.01};
021    if(mdId.equals("QFIJO")) return new double[]{0.05};
022    if(mdId.equals("QMOV")) return new double[]{0.05};
023    if(mdId.equals("SPRS")) return new double[]{0.015};
024    if(mdId.equals("SS_BB")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.068};
025    if(mdId.equals("SSBB0")) return new double[]{0.15};
026    if(mdId.equals("SSBB2")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.15};
027    if(mdId.equals("SSQF")) return new double[]{0.15, 0.4};
028    throw new IllegalArgumentException("Model " + mdId + " not found");
029  }
030
031  /**
032   * Returns increments for simulation.
033   * @param mdId Model identifier.
034   * @return Ditto.
035   */
036  public static double[] paramIncrs (String mdId) {
037    if(mdId.equals("APRX")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.005};
038    if(mdId.equals("APRX2")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.005};
039    if(mdId.equals("APRX3")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.005};
040    if(mdId.equals("ME")) return new double[]{2.0, 0.005};
041    if(mdId.equals("ME2")) return new double[]{2.0, 0.005};
042    if(mdId.equals("MM")) return new double[]{2.0, 0.005};
043    if(mdId.equals("MX_MN")) return new double[]{2.0, 0.005};
044    if(mdId.equals("QFIJO")) return new double[]{0.01};
045    if(mdId.equals("QMOV")) return new double[]{0.01};
046    if(mdId.equals("SPRS")) return new double[]{0.001};
047    if(mdId.equals("SS_BB")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.004};
048    if(mdId.equals("SSBB0")) return new double[]{0.01};
049    if(mdId.equals("SSBB2")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.01};
050    if(mdId.equals("SSQF")) return new double[]{0.01, 0.025};
051    throw new IllegalArgumentException("Model " + mdId + " not found");
052  }
053}
